---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Ordering Terms" description="Important information about quotes, availability, custom designs, collection and delivery from GyulRose Cakes." noindex={true}>
  <section class="section"><div class="container prose"><p class="eyebrow">Draft for client confirmation</p><h1>Ordering terms</h1><p>The following principles protect customers from treating an enquiry as a confirmed order. Deposit, cancellation, amendment and refund details must be supplied by the owner before deployment.</p><h2>Enquiries and bookings</h2><p>A website or WhatsApp enquiry does not reserve a date. An order is confirmed only after GyulRose accepts the design, date, fulfilment arrangements and final price under the agreed payment process.</p><h2>Prices</h2><p>Website prices are starting guides. Size, tiers, ingredients, decoration, toppers, flowers, delivery and setup can change the final quote.</p><h2>Designs</h2><p>Reference photographs communicate a direction. Handmade cakes can contain natural variation, and a previous cake is not a guarantee of an identical reproduction.</p><h2>Collection and delivery</h2><p>Times, address details, delivery availability, charges and safe handover requirements must be agreed for each order.</p><h2>Client information still required</h2><ul><li>Deposit amount and payment deadline</li><li>Cancellation and refund policy</li><li>Order amendment deadline</li><li>Minimum notice and rush-order policy</li><li>Responsibility after collection</li><li>Complaint and remedy process</li></ul></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
